thing.title: European wall outlet (non-french, non-british version)
thing.author: antifuchs
thing.description: This is a design for a wall outlet cover that should work for most of continental Europe. The model closely resembles the outlets that I have in my home.Thanks to Allan Ecker for writingblog.thingiverse.com/2009/05/04/the-personal-fab-age-hardware-store/, which inspired me to do this.
